# Loon Rule List (APPLE / Optimized for MY + China Routing)

# -----------------------
# MUST be DIRECT (Core connectivity)
# -----------------------

# Captive portal detection
DOMAIN,captive.apple.com

# APNs (push notifications - latency sensitive)
DOMAIN,push.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,push.apple.com

# Apple DNS (avoid resolution issues)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,apple-dns.net


# -----------------------
# China-specific Apple services (Route via China Proxy)
# ⚠️ Requires a "China Proxy" policy group
# -----------------------

DOMAIN-SUFFIX,apple.com.cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,icloud.com.cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cn.apple.com

# Apple Maps data (China region)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gspe1-ssl.ls.apple.com


# -----------------------
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT include global Apple domains here
# -----------------------
# ❗ Avoid adding the following:
# - apple.com
# - icloud.com
# - cdn-apple.com
# - icloud-content.com
#
# 👉 These should be handled in your main rule section
#    (e.g., Proxy / US / CN routing strategies)